      <title>比特币对冲基金的几乎无风险交易正在卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bitcoin-hedge-funds-just-about-risk-free-trade-is-roaring-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币价格创纪录的迅猛上涨，使得加密对冲基金最受欢迎的交易之一比平时更加​​有利可图，并可能有助于推动原始数字货币达到曾经不可思议的高度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bitcoin-hedge-funds-just-about-risk-free-trade-is-roaring-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 17:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
